cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper discusses the security solutions for IoT systems based on machine learning techniques, which involves the use of algorithms and models to learn from data and make predictions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the use of supervised, unsupervised, and reinforcement learning, which are subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also focuses on the authentication, access control, secure offloading, and malware detection schemes, which are related to network security (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
